      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 is a commercial CFD code with a documented software quality assurance process including regression testing and version-controlled releases. At MRL 2, Gradation 2 is required and achieved: solver provenance is fully traceable and QA documentation is available."
