        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Numerical code verification acceptance criteria for MRL 2",
        "description": "Solver passes published benchmark problems for incompressible Navier-Stokes flow (lid-driven cavity, Poiseuille flow) with second-order spatial convergence confirmed. Gradation 2 requires documented benchmark results for the relevant physics class."
      },
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent has been verified against standard benchmark problems for incompressible viscous flow relevant to blood pump simulation. Published verification studies (FDA CFD challenge) confirm second-order spatial accuracy. Gradation 2 is met."
