        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Discretization error acceptance criteria for MRL 2",
        "description": "Mesh convergence study performed on three systematically refined meshes (2.1M, 5.8M, 14.6M cells) using Richardson extrapolation. Grid convergence index (GCI) for hemolysis index < 5% on the medium mesh. Gradation 2 requires a documented mesh sensitivity study; Gradation 3 requires GCI < 5%."
      },
      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was conducted on the FDA centrifugal pump geometry. Richardson extrapolation yielded GCI = 3.2% for the hemolysis index on the 5.8M-cell medium mesh, exceeding Gradation 2 requirements. The medium mesh was selected for production runs, achieving Gradation 3."
    },
    {
