        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Output comparison acceptance criteria for MRL 2",
        "description": "CFD-predicted hemolysis index compared against experimental measurements across 5 operating points. Agreement within 15% for all points, with mean absolute error < 10%. Gradation 2 requires quantitative comparison with documented error metrics."
      },
      "rationale": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) was compared against experimental measurements at all 5 operating points. Mean absolute percentage error was 8.4%, within the 15% acceptance threshold. Gradation 2 is met with documented error metrics."
