      "rationale": "At MRL 2, numerical solver error is subsumed by the numerical code verification factor for commercial solvers with documented benchmark performance. Separate assessment of solver error beyond code verification is not required at this model risk level per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1 guidance."
    },
    {
