      "rationale": "Use error assessment is scoped out at MRL 2. The simulation was performed by a single experienced analyst team following a documented simulation protocol. At MRL 2, independent re-simulation or inter-analyst variability study is not required per ASME V&V 40-2018."
    },
    {
