      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Formal model input uncertainty propagation is scoped out at MRL 2. Nominal fluid properties (viscosity, density) and geometric dimensions are taken from FDA specifications with negligible manufacturing tolerance impact on hemolysis prediction at this risk level."
