      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Test sample characterization (device-to-device geometric variability of physical test articles) is scoped out at MRL 2. The FDA experimental campaign used a single precision-machined pump specimen; sample variability assessment is not required at this model risk level."
